\" /><br />\n因為唔係自由市場，未補地價(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未補地價要同房屋署申請<br />\n在唔在生轉都要申請<br />\n<br />\n利申之前做房屋署</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉o左名<br />\n個名好似無得再申請公屋/居屋<br />\n係咪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4619fc8c08492736f3b164b06b98915ea2698e6d","tid":367160,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:45:53.000Z","msg":"補返地價當遺產處理"},{"pid":"c2ee922b9d7c04d10b76350b72e9386164c0eeda","tid":367160,"uid":5372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:47:43.000Z","msg":"買左點會收番呀<br />\n買左既公屋都係私人物業黎架嘛<br />\nbtw 都係打1823問下清楚d"}]}